trans-unit.source: Marks the attributed method as an <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Markerar attributed metoden som en <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""> </xref> objekt.
Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: If `AutoComplete` is specified, it must not be disabled in the COM+ catalog; if enabled in the COM+ catalog, it must be specified on the component.
trans-unit.target: Om `AutoComplete` är det får inte vara inaktiverat i COM +-katalogen; som angetts om aktiverad i COM +-katalogen, det måste anges på komponenten.

trans-unit.source: The transaction automatically calls <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ContextUtil.SetComplete%2A> if the method call returns normally.
If the method call throws an exception, the transaction is aborted.
trans-unit.target: Om metodanropet genererar ett undantag, avbröts transaktionen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute"></xref> class, specifying that the application should automatically call <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ContextUtil.SetComplete*> if the transaction completes successfully.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute"> </xref> klassen som anger att programmet automatiskt ska anropa <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ContextUtil.SetComplete*>Om transaktionen har slutförts.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ContextUtil.SetComplete*>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute"></xref> class, specifying whether COM+ <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""></xref> is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute"> </xref> class, ange om COM + <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""> </xref> är aktiverad.

trans-unit.source: Specifying a parameter value of `false` causes the `AutoComplete` attribute to be ignored.
trans-unit.target: Ange ett parametervärde på `false` orsakar den `AutoComplete` attributet ignoreras.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to enable <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""></xref> in the COM+ object; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Så här aktiverar du <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""> </xref> i COM +-objektet, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating the setting of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""></xref> option in COM+.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger inställningen för den <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""> </xref> alternativet i COM +.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""></xref> is enabled in COM+; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""> </xref> är aktiverad i COM +, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
